 src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但佢地都好撚正！"},{"pid":"17134feaed6e29bf5979f0318a83cea37f847c0d","tid":217481,"uid":23619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T12:44:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>不過我個人既話，一定會揀maniac個vocal Jason<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nmetalcore嘅話應該未考慮住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n諗住打好底先～<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但佢地都好撚正！</blockquote><br />\nJason果隻聲我自己學緊，佢隻聲係fry scream再加啲野<br />\n分唔到咩scream好正常，咩真聲帶假聲帶，又咩真聲加真假音呢啲火星文，我本身讀bio 都睇到一頭霧水<br />\n要學點分既話，上去youtube 搵&quot;scream tutorial&quot;睇多啲，聽多啲就自然識分<br />\n<br />\n同埋一隻聲難唔難學係因人而異，同埋係唔關聽落去有幾「恆」事<br />\n我一開始就係想學jason把聲，明明人地話難學，但我又覺得幾易上手<br />\n<br />\n所以最重要都係揀一隻你想練既聲去做第一個目標"},{"pid":"c87cfed44658bf0adcfae52eda1c125bb3b3f893","tid":217481,"uid":87059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T15:26:45.000Z","msg":"其實scream呢樣嘢好難講， 有時候你想學fry，但偏偏就摸唔到個竅門。<br />\n<br />\n你問我嘅話 ，我嘅意見係 首先一定要知道自己想學邊一類scream多啲， 知道自己想要嘅係乜嘢。 所以自己要上網聽多啲，搵多啲。 另外，我覺得搵師傅呢一啲 係好閑嘅事。 因為每個師傅都有唔同嘅教法 ，有人buy,有人唔buy ,最緊要睇你覺得佢幫唔幫到你。 即使有一啲師傅 fry或者false chord好勁都好 ，佢幫唔到你，而你亦都摸唔到個竅門，其實都係冇乜嘢用。 所以學scream呢家嘢，真係好多因素 ，話唔埋你而家想學fry， 反而後期會學咗false chord。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n當然啦，9 up左咁耐，仲有一樣最重要嘅就係睇你夠唔夠努力，會唔會肯去練嘢，正如頭先 巴打所講， 學scream呢一樣嘢，唔同學其他樂器 ，學一年半載都未必會掌握到技巧。 但係我始終相信， 如果夠努力嘅話，終有一日一定會摸到個竅門， 會得到自己想要嘅成果。 加油呀！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：過來人"},{"pid":"839627cd58ddf6a09a0561e8694ca1f3017cead6","tid":217481,"uid":47055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T16:11:27.000Z","msg":"女仔scream我諗起香港隊M4<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />勁難聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec6526ed71c69b4e0090a1993d14eaf75795e604","tid":217481,"uid":111718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T20:20:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>不過我個人既話，一定會揀maniac個vocal Jason<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nmetalcore嘅話應該未考慮住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n諗住打好底先～<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但佢地都好撚正！</blockquote><br />\nJason果隻聲我自己學緊，佢隻聲係fry scream再加啲野<br />\n分唔到咩scream好正常，咩真聲帶假聲帶，又咩真聲加真假音呢啲火星文，我本身讀bio 都睇到一頭霧水<br />\n要學點分既話，上去youtube 搵&quot;scream tutorial&quot;睇多啲，聽多啲就自然識分<br />\n<br />\n同埋一隻聲難唔難學係因人而異，同埋係唔關聽落去有幾「恆」事<br />\n我一開始就係想學jason把聲，明明人地話難學，但我又覺得幾易上手<br />\n<br />\n所以最重要都係揀一隻你想練既聲去做第一個目標</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好！明白！多謝指點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmo